body_html:
The messages simply say that TensorFlow can run faster on your machine, if you build from sources.
They are only warning messages, which will only print once in your programs.
When using prebuilt pip packages, we aim maximum compatibility, so users with newer CPUs will see such messages.

body:
The messages simply say that TensorFlow can run faster on your machine, if you build from sources.
They are only warning messages, which will only print once in your programs.
When using prebuilt pip packages, we aim maximum compatibility, so users with newer CPUs will see such messages.
